Arsene Wenger: &quot;It's very emotional. It's the last time and it's such a long time. Such a big love story, and of course you don't want to end it - but everything comes to an end.&quot; #AFC #Arsenal  (Sky Sports)<br />
<br />
Wenger: &quot;I think it's a season of contrast, we've won 15 of 19 home games and have scored a lot of goals - it might be our best home season in my 22 years. But it didn't end like we wanted it.&quot;
